Package model

Class Calendar

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Calendar
  • public class Calendar
extends java.lang.Object
    Calendar object that contains special dates that have special prices. Eg. Weekends, holidays. holArr contains holiday dates. weekendArr contains weekend dates.
    Since:
    2019-11-09
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Lim Wai Leong, Oh Jun Teng, Edhie Wahidin Michelle, Myat Hmu Khin
